{"tid":454171,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IOS 11.2 集中白老鼠區","createTime":"2017-11-01T01:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T11:38:42.000Z","uid":26860,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"80006acfd30449a8349b8050c0922e59e07dbe69","tid":454171,"uid":26860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"暫時用落無咩特別大問題<br />\n<br />\n佢更新啲嘢對我嚟講用唔著<br />\n<br />\n控制中心的音樂控制器封面變成正方形<br />\n觸控 App Store 搜尋結果會反白<br />\n修正計算機 App 算式符號輸入遲緩問題<br />\n新增 TV App 通知設定（美國專用）<br />\nEmoji 圖示變得更清晰<br />\nLive Photo 效果載入動畫更新<br />\n按兩次 Power 鍵不再鎖定裝置<br />\n在現有或舊裝置支援 iPhone 8/X 桌布<br />\n訊息 App 內的相機 App 圖示修正<br />\n新增 AirPlay 2 介面令你可以控制其他 AirPlay 裝置例如 Apple TV 的音樂和影片<br />\n<br />\n大家有無發現咩Bugs ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/092916_20b9300d769798362516335642043158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F092916_20b9300d769798362516335642043158.jpg&h=8cbd0bfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2837f7299a218abe4fdec092132c648e20e100a","tid":454171,"uid":10101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T01:53:02.000Z","msg":"天文台彈app"},{"pid":"43cb65be77380aa6e5ea86e084f561d18a4f2deb","tid":454171,"uid":35233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:13:54.000Z","msg":"入APPLE STORE 逼人開藍芽"},{"pid":"77375c14e38170c1d09b857d576081a8bc229e01","tid":454171,"uid":35233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入APP STORE 逼人開藍芽</blockquote>"},{"pid":"696979fedf922ba287cc14ece23baf5216de9483","tid":454171,"uid":37064,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcf7cc3e42b584997364690a00f282b1c5c55dc7","tid":454171,"uid":26860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:11