 orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> iOS 11.1好多BUGS<br />\n<br />\n1) 去Phone 如果save完一個電話號碼 Keypad不能即時show到個電話號碼係聯絡人 要出去再入返Phone先至正確顯示到<br />\n<br />\n2) Siri Dictation用用下會令左上角有spinning wheel 永遠不會停<br />\n<br />\n3) iOS本身個相機Camera一開會freeze 如果轉去Video就通常無問題<br />\n<br />\n4) App Store如果有新apps要更新 永遠唔會提你 要你自己手動狂check<br />\n<br />\n5) Standby mode時候 有時撳Home button部iPhone無反應 好似crash咗咁</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦你</blockquote><br />\n割包皮啦你</blockquote><br />\n你真係好撚煩<br />\n11.2你講11.1既野托咩"},{"pid":"d29499a03fdebddc4e9c1f6ab6b7b4b6d223b082","tid":454171,"uid":37064,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5a455761c20eeeb9673bbc2a83366d2926da7d1","tid":454171,"uid":13059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文台彈app</blockquote><br />\n用到無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694f30acd01ec824a2ff72c3ac8653e2b6cafdaf","tid":454171,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"個鍵盤地球🌍位個bug整返好未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升咗11.1都重係咁..."},{"pid":"34f97040f9e0854d598f2184b73174022420b5e7","tid":454171,"uid":37064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:25:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72f1467de8846ed8762ccb7c15ec28b65c366135","tid":454171,"uid":604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/224526_f36622a83095e72bbe86bcdd025c076a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F224526_f36622a83095e72bbe86bcdd025c076a.jpg&h=215037af&s={SIZE}\" />目前最大問題，每次開mon都係咁"},{"pid":"48338f962ce719051d0a63cf6f93ae2a3f0f3ceb","tid":454171,"uid":33503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,